<Base title="Hit Me With Your Car — Michalina Sablik">
  <div class="container page-content">
    <h1>Hit Me With Your Car</h1>
    <p class="exhibition-detail-venue">Galeria Promocyjna | 2023</p>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-body">
      <p>Explores contemporary catastrophe through film and painting. A speeding car metaphorically represents our current moment—accelerating toward disaster yet trapped in slow-motion collapse. Examines how internet culture reflects collective resignation toward ecological, political, and economic crises. Pa&#322;ucha's paintings employ manipulated found footage, creating a "stream of consciousness" from online sources. Radzewicz contributes VR films and installations exploring automation and late-capitalist systems. Documents violence against women through manipulated protest footage and pornographic stills.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-detail-credits">
      <p><strong>Artists:</strong> Zofia Pa&#322;ucha, Laura Radzewicz</p>
      <p><strong>Curator:</strong> Michalina Sablik</p>
      <p><strong>Coordination:</strong> Kaja Werbanowska</p>
      <p><strong>Partners:</strong> Dom Kultury Praga</p>
    </div>
    <div class="exhibition-gallery" style="margin-top: 2.5rem; display: grid; gap: 1rem;">
